OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain or drizzle, heavy at
OL,7,Ffirst in the Borders. Becoming mainly
OL,8,Fdry during the afternoon with some
OL,9,Fbright spells coming through later
OL,10,Ftowards the west coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be mostly cloudy
OL,13,Fduring the evening and overnight with
OL,14,Fa few light showers around. Some clear
OL,15,Fspells developing later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FThe odd shower around at
OL,18,Ffirst, otherwise a largely dry day
OL,19,Fwith good sunny spells. A few showers
OL,20,Farriving in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
